                </imageobject>
            </inlinemediaobject>
        </para>
        <itemizedlist>
            <listitem>
                <para>
                    <emphasis role="bold">deltaPhi [rad] : Fixed rotation of left flange with respect to right flange (= flange_b.phi - flange_a.phi)</emphasis>
                </para>
                <para> Properties : Type 'vec' of size 1. </para>
                <para> Default value : 0</para>
            </listitem>
